//////////////////////////////////////////////////
//           requirements implemented           //
//////////////////////////////////////////////////
1. Users are able to register an account;
2. Users are able to login/logout from the system;
3. Registered users are able to create a poll;
4. Registered users are able to manage their polls
   (change the Poll's name if anyone has not voted on it);
5. Polls contain one image and several possible answers;
6. Users are able to list, search and answer to polls;
7. One user can't answer twice to the same poll;
8. Poll owners and users that already answered a poll,
   are able to see the poll results.


//////////////////////////////////////////////////
//              extra requirements              //
//////////////////////////////////////////////////
1. Poll owners are able to decide if the poll is
   public or private;
2. Private polls don't appear in listings or searches
   (Only the poll URL should needed to access it);
3. Polls can have more than one question;
4. Possibility to share a poll using email.


